<div align='center'><font size='4'><b>TIS BETTER TO GIVE</b></font><br>
<img src='http://graphics.millsberry.com/site_gfx/interiors/gazette/gazette_20071206.jpg' border='1'>
</div>
<div id='gazette_byline''><em>By Audrey Smythe-Wei<br>Editor-in-chief</em></div>
<b>Thursday, December  6, 2007</b> &mdash; The holiday season is now officially in gear, and among many things, it means it&#039;s time to start shopping for gifts. <br><br>Luckily for you, we have several tricks and tips, along with a few new hot items hitting Millsberry this week, to help you find that one-of-a-kind gift that will make someone&#039;s holiday truly special. With the addition of the package delivery service at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/post_office/">Millsberry Post Office</a>, gift giving has become much easier.<br><br>The first thing to remember is to keep an ear out and listen for any useful information that may help coming up with the perfect gift idea. If you overhear a friend talking about how they really want to throw a dance party you&#039;ll definitely want to look into the brand new Disco Dance Floor that&#039;s now available at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=12">Home Entertainment Superstore</a>.<br>
<br>
You can also always think about what someone really enjoys, and then find something to compliment it. If a friend really loves watching movies, they might like getting the new Popcorn Tin, available at <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=3">Millsberry Furniture Store</a>.<br><br>Knowing your friend&#039;s likes and dislikes also goes a long way. For instance, if they have a thing for Mr. Claus, they&#039;ll absolutely flip out over their new Santa Beard and Glasses available at <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">Wearhouse</a>, the clothing store by L. Rivers. <br><br>If you have a friend who&#039;s sentimental, they&#039;ll really appreciate the new Digital Picture Frame that shows images from some of the amazing things that happened in Millsberry during 2007. The picture frame is available at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=12">Home Entertainment Superstore</a>.<br><br>Taking hobbies into account is also a good idea. For example, if a friend is into horticulture and gardening they&#039;ll probably get a kick out of the brand new Dancing Flower now available at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=7">Tricks,Toys and Games</a>.<br><br>Remember, it&#039;s the thought that counts. Giving someone a thoughtful gift will always be appreciated, and the feeling you get from making someone&#039;s face light up with excitement will be one you will definitely not forget. Give, and you will certainly receive. <br><br><br></div>
